        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The annual income of the applicant/applicant&#39;s guardian should not exceed Rs.60,000/-.\n1. The applicant should be an Indian citizen.\n1. Applicant should be a permanent resident of Uttar Pradesh or be a resident of the state for at least 5 years\n1. Should not be guilty in any criminal case.\n\n",
